<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="around-adv">around <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'raʊnd/    美 /ə'raʊnd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在附近；在周围：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He looked around but could see nothing. 
他向四周张望，但什么也没有看到。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>各处；到处：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Children were running around on the sand.
孩子们在沙滩上跑来跑去。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-about">3.★ <strong>大约 (about)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It cost me around $10. 
这个东西花了我大约10美元。</p></div></div>